parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to lose power, hesitate, or jerk while shifting, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
The failure of the drive shaft can cause the vehicle to vibrate, shake, or lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
The failure of the airbag module can cause the airbag to deploy unexpectedly or not deploy at all in the event of a crash, leading to serious injury or death.
The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to stall, lose power, or experience unusual behavior, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
The failure of the clutch hydraulic system can cause the clutch pedal to stick to the floor, making it difficult or impossible to shift gears, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
clutch pedal sticks to the floor

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause a range of problems, including loss of power, failure of essential systems, and even fires, which can lead to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle may experience intermittent electrical failures
failure of the radio and other accessories

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the wiring harness can cause electrical shorts, fires, and loss of essential systems, which can lead to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle may experience electrical failures
and difficulty starting the engine. In some cases
the wiring harness may melt or catch fire
leading to a more serious safety risk.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the body control module can cause a range of problems, including loss of power, failure of essential systems, and even fires, which can lead to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle may experience intermittent electrical failures
and difficulty starting the engine. In some cases
the body control module may catch fire
leading to a more serious safety risk.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the battery can cause the vehicle to stall or become stranded, which can lead to accidents, injuries, or fatalities, especially if the vehicle is stranded in a hazardous location.
symptoms: The vehicle may experience difficulty starting the engine
or the battery may drain excessively
leading to a loss of power.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to the deployment of airbags in non-emergency situations, failure to deploy airbags in emergency situations, or false warnings, which can cause accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: Airbag warning light on the dashboard
failure to deploy airbags in emergency situations

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag wiring harness can cause the airbag system to malfunction, leading to false warnings, deployment of airbags in non-emergency situations, or failure to deploy airbags in emergency situations, which can cause accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: Airbag warning light on the dashboard
failure to deploy airbags in emergency situations

failure to deploy airbags in emergency situations
